
ic:(?ExprX >= ?ExprY)

   ExprX is greater than or equal to ExprY.

Arguments
   ExprX               Arithmetic expression
   ExprY               Arithmetic expression

Type
   library(ic)

Description

   Constrains ExprX to be greater than or equal to ExprY.
